Rachel Woods

Administrative Assistant

BS in Business Administration 

 

Hi, I’m Rachel Woods. At ATR, I provide Finance/HR admin support, which includes tasks such as processing payroll, tracking down missing timecards, handling terminations, managing etime administration, and conducting onboard auditing.

 

HOBBIES AND INTERESTS:

Walking my dog, traveling, trying new restaurants, kickboxing workouts

 

FAVORITE PLACE:

The beach!

 

INSPIRATIONAL QUOTE:

“80 percent of success is showing up.”
